    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and offers reliable transportation for someone who prioritizes function over aesthetics. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, minor door dings, and some fading on the clear coat, while the interior has visible wear on the upholstery and a few cracked trim pieces. Mechanically, the car starts and runs well, though it may soon require routine maintenance for wear-and-tear items like tires or brake pads. It is a solid, honest car that is priced to reflect its current cosmetic and mechanical state.",
