      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a refined example of automotive excellence, this vehicle has been curated for the discerning driver who values both mechanical integrity and aesthetic sophistication. Meticulously maintained and showing consistent pride of ownership, it offers a seamless blend of proven performance and interior comfort. This selection represents a premier opportunity to acquire a well-preserved asset that adheres to our rigorous standards of quality and reliability. We invite serious inquiries to experience the caliber of this exceptional offering.",
      "price": 34850.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
