    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride and it's looking for a new home. It\u2019s been super reliable for me and is still in really solid shape, both inside and out. It drives like a dream and definitely has plenty of adventures left in it! Perfect for anyone who wants a dependable, well-loved car that's ready to hit the road today. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a well-sorted 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera featuring the 3.6L M96 flat-six powerplant equipped with VarioCam Plus. This unit delivers a visceral driving experience through its 6-speed manual transaxle and a rear-wheel-drive configuration. The chassis is anchored by a multi-link rear suspension and upgraded Bilstein B6 dampers, ensuring precise turn-in and mid-corner stability. Crucial preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a documented IMS bearing retrofit and a recent cooling system overhaul with a high-flow water pump. The braking system remains sharp with factory-spec four-piston monoblock calipers and cross-drilled rotors. It represents a mechanically robust example of the 996.2 generation, ready for spirited canyon runs or daily engagement.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Reliable vehicle. Good condition. Regularly serviced. Clean interior. Clear title. Runs well.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a remarkable example of pride in ownership, offering a reliable and sophisticated driving experience. The exterior presents beautifully with a vibrant finish, showing only the light, expected character of a well-loved car that has been parked carefully and washed regularly. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and completely smoke-free; the seating surfaces are supple with only minor natural creasing, and the carpets have been protected by floor mats since day one. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health. It has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer\u2019s schedule, and I have the records to prove it. The engine pulls smoothly with no hesitation, the transmission shifts are crisp and certain, and the suspension remains tight and quiet over bumps. The tires offer plenty of seasonal life, and the braking system feels firm and responsive. Every button, switch, and digital display functions perfectly, from the ice-cold air conditioning to the premium sound system. This is a turn-key opportunity for a buyer seeking a dependable, high-quality vehicle that looks and drives like it has many years of service ahead.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
